docs {
  # Test Slack Message
  
  This endpoint sends a test message to Slack using the new API implementation with templates.
  
  ## Parameters:
  - `template`: "simple" or "custom"
  - `data`: For "simple": {title: string, body: string}, for "custom": {blocks: any[]}
  - `channel`: Channel ID (e.g., "SLACK_PRIMARY_CHANNEL")
  - `postAt`: Optional timestamp for scheduling
  
  ## Usage:
  - Test Slack integration
  - Verify bot token and channel permissions
  - Send custom messages for debugging
}
